content.body: Only three proposals made today's deadline for possible advancement at this month's TC39 meeting. Looks like it's going to be a short meeting…
i count 4 for advancement, but indeed there'll be a lot of time that could be filled with updates and discussions
It might be worth offloading some of the chartered incubator topics into plenary, if there’s lots of room. https://github.com/tc39/incubator-agendas/issues/22
